channel.title: Contentzpk Looking for Developers
channel.description:
At Contentzpk, our goal is to provide a unique experience to our players. This means that we need dedication from our entire staff, no matter what your duties are. If you feel you have a particular set of skills that you feel is important, in the success of a server fill out the form I provide below and we will see if we have something that fits your particular skills.
What skill set do you have to offer?
How long have you had this particular skill set?
Do you have proof or prior experience with another rsps?
List any other skills beyond your primary that would help make a rsps successful.
You may either reply to these questions below, email me at contentzpk@gmail.com, or add my skype suseto1989
Thank you for viewing my post i hope to hear from you soon.
Contentzpk Staff
